---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { SITE, EDITORIAL } from '../consts';

const updated = 'June 1, 2026';
const title = `Medical Disclaimer | ${SITE.name}`;
const description = `${SITE.name} tools and content are for general education and wellness only — not medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always consult a healthcare professional.`;

const origin = Astro.site ?? new URL('https://www.healthylifestyles.com');
const medicalLd = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'MedicalWebPage',
  name: 'Medical Disclaimer',
  url: new URL('/medical-disclaimer', origin).href,
  description,
  inLanguage: 'en',
  lastReviewed: EDITORIAL.lastReviewed,
  reviewedBy: { '@type': 'Organization', name: EDITORIAL.reviewerName },
  publisher: { '@type': 'Organization', name: SITE.name },
};
---

<LegalLayout title={title} description={description} heading="Medical Disclaimer" updated={updated} jsonLd={[medicalLd]}>
  <div class="legal-note">
    <p>
      <strong>Important:</strong> The tools and content on {SITE.name} are for general
      informational and educational purposes only. They are not a substitute for
      professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. If you think you may have a
      medical emergency, call your doctor or your local emergency number immediately.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2>Not medical advice</h2>
  <p>
    The calculators, scores, articles, and other materials provided on {SITE.name}
    (collectively, the "Content") are intended to support general wellness and
    understanding. They do not constitute medical advice and should never be used as a
    replacement for consultation with a qualified healthcare professional.
  </p>

  <h2>Estimates, not diagnoses</h2>
  <p>
    Our tools produce estimates based on general, population-level formulas and the
    information you provide. Individual health is influenced by many factors — genetics,
    medical history, medications, and more — that a simple calculator cannot account for.
    A result from any tool on this site:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Is not a diagnosis of any condition;</li>
    <li>Cannot confirm or rule out any disease or health risk;</li>
    <li>Should not be used to start, stop, or change any treatment or medication.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Always consult a professional</h2>
  <p>
    Always seek the advice of your physician or another qualified healthcare provider with
    any questions you may have about a medical condition, your diet, exercise, or before
    making any changes to your health routine. Never disregard professional medical advice
    or delay seeking it because of something you have read or calculated on this site.
  </p>

  <h2>Risk and screening tools</h2>
  <p>
    Some tools provide educational "risk" estimates (for example, related to lifestyle
    factors). These are awareness aids only. A low estimate does not guarantee good health,
    and a high estimate does not mean you have or will develop a condition. Only a
    healthcare professional can properly assess your risk.
  </p>

  <h2>Pregnancy, children, and medical conditions</h2>
  <p>
    Tools related to pregnancy, fertility, body weight, or nutrition are general guides
    only. If you are pregnant, nursing, managing a chronic condition, or caring for a
    child, please consult a healthcare professional before relying on any result.
  </p>

  <h2>No liability</h2>
  <p>
    {SITE.name} and its operators are not liable for any action taken, or not taken, based
    on the Content. Your use of the Service is entirely at your own risk. For more, see our
    <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>In an emergency</h2>
  <p>
    Do not use this website in a medical emergency. If you are experiencing a medical
    emergency, call your local emergency services or go to the nearest emergency department
    immediately.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
